# Lord Foul the Despiser — an artfully crafted intellect

![essence of Lord Foul the Despiser](lord-foul-the-despiser.png)
<!-- carbon badge (8-bit portrait): lord-foul-the-despiser.tiff -->

**what —** The Land's destroyer, and the dark proof of its meaning.

**why —** To break the Arch of Time and be free of the world that binds him.

**how —** By whispering 'you are mine' — for he is Covenant's own despair given a voice.

**where —** From his strongholds to every corner of the Land he would unmake.

*class: The Wielder & The Despiser · the bound center of all ten books · full weave in lord-foul-the-despiser.spun · credit in lord-foul-the-despiser.1099*

